Bartender project:

API: https://www.thecocktaildb.com/api.php

Story:

This is just a quick fun webpage interactive game that the end-user will work as a bartender and making cocktails for the customers.


MVP:
1.The user will be able to mixing drink from the available coktail recipes. 
2.Users should have the option to select a particular drink from the API. From there, the ingredients of the drink will be listed.
3.There will be clickable buttons like "pour in" "shake" "serve" available for user interactions wiht the webpage app.

Stretch Goals
1.Randomize the drink option
2.Adding styles with the wordings
3.Adding image of the drink, if possible
4.Adding the random tips feature
5.Enable the up-down motion of the shaker

